                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-1855-18430612 t18430612-1855-punishment-124"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">THOMAS VICKERS</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18430612-1855-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
